name: Ferntastic
description:
Introduction

Easy access and 2 rappels make this quick and low commitment canyon worthwhile.

Please tread lightly and be mindful of the moss and other vegetation.

Approach

Park off the 89A and walk a short distance from the road to the start of the canyon drainage.

Descent

R1: 80' off pinch near edge.

R2: 25' off pinch near edge. Can be avoided LDC to gain social trail to Pumphouse Wash and exit trail.

Exit

We found a social trail back up to the rim and our vehicles, located just up Pumphouse Wash a couple hundred feet on the left.

Red tape

Beta sites

Trip reports and media

Background

This canyon had been prevoously explored but not documented. New anchors placed 7/25/22.
